{"tid":1152041,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"「轉載」曼聯球迷季尾最精彩","createTime":"2019-05-12T17:03:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-12T17:21:01.000Z","uid":119157,"like":39,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"cd5b3d861e8b3151a54876292a2b974f21d9bafb","tid":1152041,"uid":119157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T17:03:48.000Z","msg":"無歐聯，球員星散，領隊無料，煞科日可以點面對？正常人都係繼續撐自己隊波，打返場好波。曼聯迷呢？<br />\n<br />\n今晚佢地只會關心白禮頓輸同狼隊贏。曼城係同市宿敵，利物浦就係世仇。兩隊爭冠，皇者曼聯只能哀求上天賜冠給同市宿敵，好讓利物浦繼續29年無冠。但係曼城由昔日弱者幾年間同皇者曼相差18個level，曼聯迷從無恥辱感，還繼續樂在其中，共享同市光榮。<br />\n<br />\n然後捱過煞科日，曼聯迷球季還未完結，佢地會繼續支持曼城贏足總盃，避免屈福特打歐霸而令皇者曼聯提早打第二圈外圍賽。<br />\n<br />\n捱過足總盃，曼聯迷就會化身車路士球迷，寄望車路士歐霸打敗阿仙奴，令自己不會成為Big six唯一一隊缺席歐聯的隊伍。<br />\n<br />\n幾日後，曼聯迷就會做熱剌球迷，希望力阻利物浦六度歐冠封王。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2b43c43104c2f9eaf72e33a500f870167f3345f","tid":1152041,"uid":5191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T17:05:04.000Z","msg":"過唔到2個回覆"},{"pid":"169fcb70c5f476437cdfd1b8dbe48b6a04381fe6","tid":1152041,"uid":119157,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T17:05:51.000Z","msg":"原來主場輸鳩埋比卡迪夫城0:2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51700a0112efaadfbddfc2e47276c0a8624dee6a","tid":1152041,"uid":5649,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"169fcb70c5f476437cdfd1b8dbe48b6a04381fe6","tid":1152041,"uid":119157,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T17:05:51.000Z","msg":"原來主場輸鳩埋比卡迪夫城0:2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"h